The problem with adjusting loot value too fast is this.<br>
<br>
Item drops for 40 points, people with low dkp bid and point hoarders dont because they know the item will drop in points soon. So then the person with low dkp wins but then drops even lower. <br>
<br>
Then the item is dropped in points because hoarders are letting it rot. THEN the hoarders bid at say... 20 points. They then keep their lead 2x as much as the people who are actually using the system the right way.<br>
